t, and how we keep it safe.\\n\\nWe don't sell your data. We don't use it for advertising. We use it to run your agent and improve the service.\"}],\"$undefined\",\"$undefined\"]}],[\"$\",\"section\",\"what-we-collect\",{\"id\":\"what-we-collect\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mb-5 flex items-center gap-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"style\":{\"fontFamily\":\"var(--font-jetbrains), 'JetBrains Mono', monospace\",\"color\":\"var(--g)\",\"fontSize\":11,\"letterSpacing\":\"0.05em\"},\"children\":\"02\"}],[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"font-extrabold\",\"style\":{\"fontSize\":\"1.2rem\",\"color\":\"#F0F7F1\",\"letterSpacing\":\"-0.02em\"},\"children\":\"What we collect\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"style\":{\"flex\":1,\"height\":0.5,\"background\":\"rgba(74,143,93,0.18)\"}}]]}],\"$undefined\",\"$undefined\",[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-2 space-y-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",\"Account information\",{\"className\":\"rounded-xl p-4\",\"style\":{\"background\":\"var(--surface2)\",\"border\":\"0.5px solid rgba(74,143,93,0.12)\"},\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mb-1 text-sm font-bold\",\"style\":{\"color\":\"#E8F0E9\",\"letterSpacing\":\"-0.01em\"},\"children\":\"Account information\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm leading-relaxed\",\"style\":{\"color\":\"rgba(134,201,148,0.6)\",\"lineHeight\":1.7},\"children\":\"Your email address and username when you register. Used to identify your account and send service-related communications.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"Agent configuration\",{\"className\":\"rounded-xl p-4\",\"style\":{\"background\":\"var(--surface2)\",\"border\":\"0.5px solid rgba(74,143,93,0.12)\"},\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mb-1 text-sm font-bold\",\"style\":{\"color\":\"#E8F0E9\",\"letterSpacing\":\"-0.01em\"},\"children\":\"Agent configuration\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm leading-relaxed\",\"style\":{\"color\":\"rgba(134,201,148,0.6)\",\"lineHeight\":1.7},\"children\":\"Settings you configure for your agent — integrations, preferences, and connected services. Stored to run your agent correctly.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"Usage data\",{\"className\":\"rounded-xl p-4\",\"style\":{\"background\":\"var(--surface2)\",\"border\":\"0.5px solid rgba(74,143,93,0.12)\"},\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mb-1 text-sm font-bold\",\"style\":{\"color\":\"#E8F0E9\",\"letterSpacing\":\"-0.01em\"},\"children\":\"Usage data\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm leading-relaxed\",\"style\":{\"color\":\"rgba(134,201,148,0.6)\",\"lineHeight\":1.7},\"children\":\"Aggregate metrics like uptime, request counts, and error rates. Used to monitor service health and improve reliability. We do not log the content of your agent's conversations.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"Billing information\",{\"className\":\"rounded-xl p-4\",\"style\":{\"background\":\"var(--surface2)\",\"border\":\"0.5px solid rgba(74,143,93,0.12)\"},\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mb-1 text-sm font-bold\",\"style\":{\"color\":\"#E8F0E9\",\"letterSpacing\":\"-0.01em\"},\"children\":\"Billing information\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm leading-relaxed\",\"style\":{\"color\":\"rgba(134,201,148,0.6)\",\"lineHeight\":1.7},\"children\":\"Handled entirely by our payment processor. We store only your plan tier and subscription status — never raw card details.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"API keys (BYOK)\",{\"className\":\"rounded-xl p-4\",\"style\":{\"background\":\"var(--surface2)\",\"border\":\"0.5px solid rgba(74,143,93,0.12)\"},\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mb-1 text-sm font-bold\",\"style\":{\"color\":\"#E8F0E9\",\"letterSpacing\":\"-0.01em\"},\"children\":\"API keys (BYOK)\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm leading-relaxed\",\"style\":{\"color\":\"rgba(134,201,148,0.6)\",\"lineHeight\":1.7},\"children\":\"If you bring your own AI API keys, they are encrypted at rest and only decrypted in memory when your agent processes a request. We never read, share, or use your keys for any purpose other than running your agent.\"}]]}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"section\",\"what-we-dont-collect\",{\"id\":\"what-we-dont-collect\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mb-5 flex items-center gap-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"style\":{\"fontFamily\":\"var(--font-jetbrains), 'JetBrains Mono', monospace\",\"color\":\"var(--g)\",\"fontSize\":11,\"letterSpacing\":\"0.05em\"},\"children\":\"03\"}],[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"font-extrabold\",\"style\":{\"fontSize\":\"1.2rem\",\"color\":\"#F0F7F1\",\"letterSpacing\":\"-0.02em\"},\"children\":\"What we don't collect\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"style\":{\"flex\":1,\"height\":0.5,\"background\":\"rgba(74,143,93,0.18)\"}}]]}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm leading-relaxed\",\"style\":{\"color\":\"rgba(134,201,148,0.65)\",\"lineHeight\":1.85,\"whiteSpace\":\"pre-line\"},\"children\":\"We do not read, log, or store the content of conversations between you and your agent beyond what is needed for the immediate request. Your messages, tasks, and outputs are yours.\\n\\nWe do not collect biometric data, location data, or any data from third-party sources beyond what you explicitly connect to your agent.\"}],\"$undefined\",\"$undefined\"]}],[\"$\",\"section\",\"data-storage\",{\"id\":\"data-storage\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mb-5 flex items-center gap-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"style\":{\"fontFamily\":\"var(--font-jetbrains), 'JetBrains Mono', monospace\",\"color\":\"var(--g)\",\"fontSize\":11,\"letterSpacing\":\"0.05em\"},\"children\":\"04\"}],[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"font-extrabold\",\"style\":{\"fontSize\":\"1.2rem\",\"color\":\"#F0F7F1\",\"letterSpacing\":\"-0.02em\"},\"children\":\"Data storage & security\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"style\":{\"flex\":1,\"height\":0.5,\"background\":\"rgba(74,143,93,0.18)\"}}]]}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm leading-relaxed\",\"style\":{\"color\":\"rgba(134,201,148,0.65)\",\"lineHeight\":1.85,\"whiteSpace\":\"pre-line\"},\"children\":\"Your agent runs on dedicated infrastructure — not shared containers. Your data is isolated to your instance by default.\\n\\nAll data is encrypted in transit (TLS) and at rest (AES-256). API keys and credentials are stored in encrypted vaults. We follow industry-standard security practices and conduct regular security reviews.\\n\\nInfrastructure is hosted on Hetzner data centers in the EU. If you require a specific data residency region, contact us.\"}],\"$undefined\",\"$undefined\"]}],[\"$\",\"section\",\"third-parties\",{\"id\":\"third-parties\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mb-5 flex items-center gap-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"style\":{\"fontFamily\":\"var(--font-jetbrains), 'JetBrains Mono', monospace\",\"color\":\"var(--g)\",\"fontSize\":11,\"letterSpacing\":\"0.05em\"},\"children\":\"05\"}],[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"font-extrabold\",\"style\":{\"fontSize\":\"1.2rem\",\"color\":\"#F0F7F1\",\"letterSpacing\":\"-0.02em\"},\"children\":\"Third-party services\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"style\":{\"flex\":1,\"height\":0.5,\"background\":\"rgba(74,143,93,0.18)\"}}]]}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm leading-relaxed\",\"style\":{\"color\":\"rgba(134,201,148,0.65)\",\"lineHeight\":1.85,\"whiteSpace\":\"pre-line\"},\"children\":\"MonkeAgent integrates with platforms you choose — Telegram, Discord, Slack, and others. When you connect a platform, that platform's own privacy policy applies to data flowing through it. We only pass data to platforms that you've explicitly authorised.\\n\\nIf you use a managed AI plan, your prompts are processed by our selected AI provider under their privacy terms. We will always disclose which provider is in use.\"}],\"$undefined\",\"$undefined\"]}],[\"$\",\"section\",\"your-rights\",{\"id\":\"your-rights\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mb-5 flex items-center gap-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"style\":{\"fontFamily\":\"var(--font-jetbrains), 'JetBrains Mono', monospace\",\"color\":\"var(--g)\",\"fontSize\":11,\"letterSpacing\":\"0.05em\"},\"children\":\"06\"}],[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"font-extrabold\",\"style\":{\"fontSize\":\"1.2rem\",\"color\":\"#F0F7F1\",\"letterSpacing\":\"-0.02em\"},\"children\":\"Your rights\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"style\":{\"flex\":1,\"height\":0.5,\"background\":\"rgba(74,143,93,0.18)\"}}]]}],\"$undefined\",\"$undefined\",[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-2 space-y-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",\"Access\",{\"className\":\"rounded-xl p-4\",\"style\":{\"background\":\"var(--surface2)\",\"border\":\"0.5px solid rgba(74,143,93,0.12)\"},\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mb-1 text-sm font-bold\",\"style\":{\"color\":\"#E8F0E9\",\"letterSpacing\":\"-0.01em\"},\"children\":\"Access\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm leading-relaxed\",\"style\":{\"color\":\"rgba(134,201,148,0.6)\",\"lineHeight\":1.7},\"children\":\"Request a copy of all data we hold about you.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"Deletion\",{\"className\":\"rounded-xl p-4\",\"style\":{\"background\":\"var(--surface2)\",\"border\":\"0.5px solid rgba(74,143,93,0.12)\"},\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mb-1 text-sm font-bold\",\"style\":{\"color\":\"#E8F0E9\",\"letterSpacing\":\"-0.01em\"},\"children\":\"Deletion\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm leading-relaxed\",\"style\":{\"color\":\"rgba(134,201,148,0.6)\",\"lineHeight\":1.7},\"children\":\"Delete your account and all associated data at any time. Deletion is permanent and irreversible.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"Portability\",{\"className\":\"rounded-xl p-4\",\"style\":{\"background\":\"var(--surface2)\",\"border\":\"0.5px solid rgba(74,143,93,0.12)\"},\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mb-1 text-sm font-bold\",\"style\":{\"color\":\"#E8F0E9\",\"letterSpacing\":\"-0.01em\"},\"children\":\"Portability\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm leading-relaxed\",\"style\":{\"color\":\"rgba(134,201,148,0.6)\",\"lineHeight\":1.7},\"children\":\"Export your agent configuration and settings in a machine-readable format.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"Correction\",{\"className\":\"rounded-xl p-4\",\"style\":{\"background\":\"var(--surface2)\",\"border\":\"0.5px solid rgba(74,143,93,0.12)\"},\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mb-1 text-sm font-bold\",\"style\":{\"color\":\"#E8F0E9\",\"letterSpacing\":\"-0.01em\"},\"children\":\"Correction\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm leading-relaxed\",\"style\":{\"color\":\"rgba(134,201,148,0.6)\",\"lineHeight\":1.7},\"children\":\"Update or correct any inaccurate account information.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"Objection\",{\"className\":\"rounded-xl p-4\",\"style\":{\"background\":\"var(--surface2)\",\"border\":\"0.5px solid rgba(74,143,93,0.12)\"},\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mb-1 text-sm font-bold\",\"style\":{\"color\":\"#E8F0E9\",\"letterSpacing\":\"-0.01em\"},\"children\":\"Objection\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm leading-relaxed\",\"style\":{\"color\":\"rgba(134,201,148,0.6)\",\"lineHeight\":1.7},\"children\":\"Object to any processing of your data that goes beyond what is strictly necessary to provide the service.\"}]]}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"section\",\"retention\",{\"id\":\"retention\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mb-5 flex items-center gap-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"style\":{\"fontFamily\":\"var(--font-jetbrains), 'JetBrains Mono', monospace\",\"color\":\"var(--g)\",\"fontSize\":11,\"letterSpacing\":\"0.05em\"},\"children\":\"07\"}],[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"font-extrabold\",\"style\":{\"fontSize\":\"1.2rem\",\"color\":\"#F0F7F1\",\"letterSpacing\":\"-0.02em\"},\"children\":\"Data retention\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"style\":{\"flex\":1,\"height\":0.5,\"background\":\"rgba(74,143,93,0.18)\"}}]]}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm leading-relaxed\",\"style\":{\"color\":\"rgba(134,201,148,0.65)\",\"lineHeight\":1.85,\"whiteSpace\":\"pre-line\"},\"children\":\"We retain your data for as long as your account is active. If you cancel your subscription, your data is retained for 30 days to allow recovery, then permanently deleted.\\n\\nAggregate and anonymised usage data (e.g. total request counts with no identifying information) may be retained indefinitely for service improvement purposes.\"}],\"$undefined\",\"$undefined\"]}],[\"$\",\"section\",\"changes\",{\"id\":\"changes\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mb-5 flex items-center gap-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"style\":{\"fontFamily\":\"var(--font-jetbrains), 'JetBrains Mono', monospace\",\"color\":\"var(--g)\",\"fontSize\":11,\"letterSpacing\":\"0.05em\"},\"children\":\"08\"}],[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"font-extrabold\",\"style\":{\"fontSize\":\"1.2rem\",\"color\":\"#F0F7F1\",\"letterSpacing\":\"-0.02em\"},\"children\":\"Changes to this policy\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"style\":{\"flex\":1,\"height\":0.5,\"background\":\"rgba(74,143,93,0.18)\"}}]]}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm leading-relaxed\",\"style\":{\"color\":\"rgba(134,201,148,0.65)\",\"lineHeight\":1.85,\"whiteSpace\":\"pre-line\"},\"children\":\"We may update this policy as the service evolves. When we make material changes, we'll notify you by email and update the \\\"Last updated\\\" date below. Continued use of MonkeAgent after changes take effect constitutes acceptance of the revised policy.\"}],\"$undefined\",\"$undefined\"]}],[\"$\",\"section\",\"contact\",{\"id\":\"contact\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mb-5 flex items-center gap-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"style\":{\"fontFamily\":\"var(--font-jetbrains), 'JetBrains Mono', monospace\",\"color\":\"var(--g)\",\"fontSize\":11,\"letterSpacing\":\"0.05em\"},\"children\":\"09\"}]